Gillian Vigman https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gillian_Vigman 0 Gillian Vigman (born January 28, 1972) is an American comic actress. She is most recognizable for her role as "Jack's Wife" in many Jack in the Box commercials, but is also notable for her membership in the recurring cast of comedians on sketch comedy series MADtv. She also starred in the ABC comedy Sons Daughters, and had recurring roles in the sitcoms Suburgatory and New Girl. Gillian_Vigman ( born January_28_,_1972 ) is an_American_comic_actress .
